      "id": "n3",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 2,
      "text": "This section tests your ability to communicate orally in German in everyday situations. The oral examination takes 15 minutes total and consists of three parts."
    },
    {
      "id": "n4",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 3,
